attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles the stool, loosens the middle hex nut with the wrench, unscrews all four screws of the legs, detaches the legs from the seat, puts all the screws and saddle washer inside the plastic bag, removes the middle hex nut and bolt, and finally separates the legs and puts them on the table.
